org/877 Vietnamese (Vietnam) YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQTIZt3LMQ4&feature=emb_logo Video Library:  https://sawbo-animations.org/878 HOW TO WASH YOUR HANDS PLAYLIST
Washing hands is the best way to prevent the spread of germs and diseases. The habit of washing hands with soap and water constitutes the first line of defense against the spread of many diseases, from the common cold or diarrhea to more serious illnesses such as meningitis, influenza or hepatitis as well as many other diseases. PREVENTING SICKNESS PLAYLIST 
This animation contains a basic overview of microbial disease transmission concepts and basic ways to minimize such transmissions.